columns.name: application_name
columns.description: The name of the application to which the application version belongs.

columns.name: application_version_arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application version.

columns.name: build_arn
columns.description: Reference to the artifact from the AWS CodeBuild build.

columns.name: date_created
columns.description: The creation date of the application version.

columns.name: date_updated
columns.description: The last modified date of the application version.

columns.name: description
columns.description: The description of the application version.

columns.name: status
columns.description: The processing status of the application version. Reflects the state of the application version during its creation.

columns.name: version_label
columns.description: A unique identifier for the application version.

columns.name: source_build_information
columns.description: Information about the source code for the application version if the source code was retrieved from AWS CodeCommit.

columns.name: source_bundle
columns.description: The storage location of the application version's source bundle in Amazon S3.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags assigned to the application.

columns.name: title
columns.description: A title for the resource, typically the resource name.
